title: Supernova
overview: At the age of 30, Nicolasa, June, and Mimi face their social obligations, desires, and frustrations. The result is an explosive cocktail, a Supernova that marks a breakdown in their lives and, amidst the chaos of the explosion, in those of their families, boyfriends, and friends. But they also enjoy happy moments, where they support each other to reach the horizon they so much desire.
